WEBVTT

00:01:26.299 --> 00:01:31.523
One of every hundred
children born worldwide

00:01:31.547 --> 00:01:34.470
has some kind of heart disease.

00:01:35.214 --> 00:01:40.364
There's a part of this problem
I think I can solve --

00:01:40.388 --> 00:01:46.935
the part of this problem
I have spent my life working on.

00:01:47.904 --> 00:01:49.493
The problem starts

00:01:50.279 --> 00:01:51.636
during pregnancy.

00:01:52.610 --> 00:01:55.617
The fetus needs to survive
inside the mother.

00:01:56.808 --> 00:02:00.819
Survival depends on communication